text: Kawasaki line may refer to: * Kawasaki Kisen Kaisha () aka K-Line, a private Japanese railroad line and operating company * Kawasaki Municipal Subway (), a future subway line in Kawasaki, Kanagwa Prefecture, Japan * Kawasaki City Tram (), a former tram line in Kawasaki, Kanagwa Prefecture, Japan ==See also== *Kawasaki Route () aka Route K6, a toll road of the Shuto expressway system in Greater Tokyo
title: Kawasaki line
